#!/usr/bin/env bash
set -euo pipefail

cat >&2 <<'MSG'
The historical legacy Web Console bootstrap path is disabled in the PastureStack migration source tree.

Reason: it installed Node 6, PhantomJS, and global Bower. That toolchain is EOL and must not be used to produce maintained Web Console artifacts.

Next path: follow docs/modernization.md to replace node-sass/Bower first, then add a maintained Ubuntu 26.04 build container and browser/API regression tests before publishing a new UI artifact.
MSG
exit 2
